<div class="w-full">
  <% content_for :title, "Hello" %>

  <div class="resource-container">
    <div class="resource-header">
      <div>
        <h1 class="resource-title">Welcome!</h1>
        <p class="resource-description">The project is quirky by design, adding a unique touch to your task management experience. It's minimalistic and perfect for individual use or small teams of up to 5 people.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="divide-y divide-gray-200 dark:divide-gray-700 space-y-0">
      <div class="p-4">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-200 mb-2">Getting started</h3>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          <p>Tasks live inside projects. You can prioritize important tasks with a "star", set due date and write comments.</p>
          <p>The Personal project is your space for all personal tasks that you don't plan to share with others. Use it for tasks that don't need their own project.</p>
          <p>The Sample project is here to give you an impression of what a filled-out project looks like. It contains example data so you can explore the app's features. You can remove it when you are ready.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="p-4">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-200 mb-2">Personalization</h3>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          <p>The app supports color themes to personalize your experience. Visit your <%= link_to 'settings page', users_settings_path, class: "text-violet-700 dark:text-violet-600 underline" %> to choose from available themes.</p>
          <p>You can also customize your dark mode preference and manage your privacy settings there.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="p-4">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Enjoy using the app, and if you have any questions or need assistance visit the <a href="https://gitlab.com/dzaporozhets/microprojectapp" class="text-violet-700 dark:text-violet-600 underline">dev project page</a></p>
      </div>

      <% if current_user && Devise.mappings[:user].confirmable? && !current_user.confirmed_at %>
        <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800">
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">P.S. Check your inbox for the confirmation link. Make sure to confirm your email within an hour.</p>
        </div>
      <% end %>

      <div class="p-4">
        <%= link_to "Go to projects page", root_path, class: "btn-base" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
